INPUT Age 
INPUT Height
tired=False
WHILE tired==False
INPUT ride
IF ride==dragon rollercoaster
THEN 
  IF height>=48 AND Age>=10
  THEN 
    OUTPUT "you meet criteria for dragon rollercoaster"
    INPUT tired
  ELSE 
    OUTPUT "sorry you do not meet criteria for dragon rollercoaster"
    INPUT tired
  END IF
ELSE IF ride==SkySwing
  THEN 
    IF height>=54
  THEN 
    OUTPUT "you meet criteria for SkySwing"
    INPUT tired
  ELSE 
    OUTPUT "sorry you do not meet criteria for SkySwing"
    INPUT tired
  END IF
END IF
ELSE IF Age>=5
   THEN 
     OUTPUT "you meet criteria for The Carousel"
     INPUT tired
  ELSE 
    OUTPUT "sorry you do not meet criteria for The Carousel"
    INPUT tired
END IF
END IF
END WHILE
OUTPUT "thankyou"



My Understanding:
check requirements according to the choice of ride and output an appropriate result.
ask if they are tired after each output.repeat if they are not tired





     
